            "detailed_description": "Phantom Halls is a squad-based side-scrolling comedy-horror game. A group of teens from the Occult Studies Club set out on an assignment, but quickly find themselves attempting to survive a night in a haunted mansion...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPrepare to face the undead terrors that stalk the phantom halls! Squad up to escape alive using whatever you can find, but remember - you can’t kill what you can't see, so be sure to bring a flashlight!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Fast-paced, action-packed, squad-based gameplay<br />\r\n- Unique 3D papercraft visual style<br />\r\n- Play through the campaign in single-player or drop-in/out local co-op<br />\r\n- Various characters, quests, weapons and items to unlock<br />\r\n- Gather items and craft upgrades, from cosmetic improvements to party-wide perks<br />\r\n- Includes officially licensed Evil Dead 2 content!",
